snippet.title: Elden Ring - E3 2019 Announcement Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
A new world created by Hidetaka Miyazaki and Gerorge R.R. Martin
ELDEN RING, developed by FromSoftwareInc., is a fantasy action-RPG adventure set within a world created by Hidetaka
Miyazaki - creator of the influential Dark Souls video game series; and George R.R. Martin - author of the The New York
Times best-selling fantasy series, A song of Ice and Fire. Danger and discovery lurk around every corner in
FromSoftware's largest game to-date.
